                --- XiVO 1.2

SIP
  * tls connexions
      cert files and ca files storage directory is defined in ipbx.ini (section [tls], key 'certdir')
        cert files ends with '.pem' extensions, ca files are all others
        cadir is defined in ipbx.ini (section [tls], key 'cadir')

        defaulf directories are respectively /var/lib/asterisk/certs and /var/lib/asterisk/certs/cadir
